     C           K#GAD2    KLIST
     C                     KFLD           K@TOKU  40
     C                     KFLD           K@NONY  40
     C                     KFLD           K@NKOJ  1
     C                     KFLD           K@NUKE  4
     C           K#FBC2    KLIST
